Human Fall detection algorithim for fisheye images in indoor video sequences
based on the orientations of vectors in the image.

REQUIREMENTS
opencv>2
cmake

HOW TO USE IN LINUX
1. make new directory
2.clone the repo to your new directory
3.cd to new directory
4.cmake .
5.make -j#no of processors (to speed up the process)
6.binary dumped into the current directory

References
"A fall detection algorithm for indoor video sequences captured by fish-eye camera" kostas Delibasis ,Ilias Maglogianis

